<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/733816-dear-anyone-who-has-read-these">Dear anyone who has read these books,

Are the Characters and the stories in book one (stories 1-3) related or tied in to the stories and characters in books 2 (stories 4-6) and 3 (stories 7-9)?

Kinda need to know, but no spoilers please!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_733816'><a id="like_count_community_question_733816" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/733816?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F3099787-night-world-no-1">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/733816-dear-anyone-who-has-read-these">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/733816-dear-anyone-who-has-read-these">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
