<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1169814-my-14-year-old-wants-to-read-this-book">My 14 year old wants to read this book. Is it even remotely appropriate for her age group?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1169814'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F3099787-night-world-no-1">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1169814-my-14-year-old-wants-to-read-this-book">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1169814-my-14-year-old-wants-to-read-this-book">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/119940152-maddy"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1619790283i/119940152._UY100_CR2,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/119940152-maddy">Maddy</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">yes it is. It is very appropriate as compared to the kind of things teens are being exposed to through social media. It does not have any really distu<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">yes it is. It is very appropriate as compared to the kind of things teens are being exposed to through social media. It does not have any really disturbing images or sexual scenes. There might be some depiction of death or violence, but not to a degree that would make a 14 year old loose sleep over. If I were to say, this would be appropriate for anybody who is 12+.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
