<li class='cover' id='bookCover_6416903'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6416903-dark-secrets-1"><img alt="Dark Secrets 1 (Dark Secrets, #1-2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348222553l/6416903._SX98_.jpg" />
